    <p>As an experienced Agile delivery manager and software developer, my background is in retail management, which means clients benefit from my unique skill set to deliver public sector projects.  I seamlessly combine people management, business acumen, and technical understanding and when clients see my successful Agile project management history, they have the confidence to work with me on further key projects time and again.</p>

