    <p>I am also the founder and MD of Digital Reflow, a full-service digital consultancy, employing a team of ten, working with premium, luxury and aspirational brands to provide customer-focused digital strategies with a strong emphasis on healthy ROI.</p>

    <p>Passionate about building positive, productive relationships with my teams and the people I work with, I believe in modelling good leadership skills to raise other leaders. Being able to see the big picture and the end goal, while remaining focused on the details of each task we face, is part of what I offer. I believe in leading by example and empowering others to take responsibility in their role, supporting my teams to continuously improve the outcomes they are tasked with.</p>
